00:17:35.500 --> 00:17:38.730
And you also had these Tuareg
rebels, the nomadic rebels

00:17:38.730 --> 00:17:40.830
who had been fighting
for generations

00:17:40.830 --> 00:17:43.400
for their own independent
state in Northern Mali.

00:17:43.400 --> 00:17:45.330
They got involved
in the act too.

00:17:45.330 --> 00:17:47.500
These were secular
rebels, but they

00:17:47.500 --> 00:17:50.460
