00:17:55.860 --> 00:17:57.670
The government fell.

00:17:57.670 --> 00:18:02.080
Timbuktu fell on
April 1st, 2012.

00:18:02.080 --> 00:18:06.610
This is a photo of
a Sufi shrine, which

00:18:06.610 --> 00:18:11.180
