invaded the country.

00:19:40.070 --> 00:19:42.320
And then the whole
North became a war zone.

00:19:42.320 --> 00:19:45.250
So the final act
was the continuing

00:19:45.250 --> 00:19:48.220
the smuggling operation
as French troops

00:19:48.220 --> 00:19:52.070
and French aircraft were bombing
the hell out of the North,

00:19:52.070 --> 00:19:55.420
destroying the jihadis, but
also putting these manuscripts

00:19:55.420 --> 00:19:57.880
in grave, grave danger.

00:19:57.880 --> 00:20:01.330
These are some shots I
took about four months

00:20:01.330 --> 00:20:07.020
