00:20:14.770 --> 00:20:18.380
which was that the jihadists
grabbed every manuscript

00:20:18.380 --> 00:20:22.580
they could find that was left
in the city and burned them.

00:20:22.580 --> 00:20:25.120
And this is a picture
I took, again,

00:20:25.120 --> 00:20:26.650
about probably-- let's see.

00:20:26.650 --> 00:20:29.490
Let's say August,
2013, so about six

00:20:29.490 --> 00:20:31.430
months after the
war in the North

00:20:31.430 --> 00:20:34.040
ended and the jihadis had been
thrown out of Timbuktu and out

00:20:34.040 --> 00:20:38.030
of the cities into the desert--
