00:21:14.830 --> 00:21:17.220
And I was heading
across the Niger river

00:21:17.220 --> 00:21:22.310
to visit Timbuktu to start my
reporting on this book project.

00:21:22.310 --> 00:21:26.301
And you can see-- kind
of an interesting shot.

00:21:26.301 --> 00:21:28.550
Guy over here thinks he's
